Very experienced raiders may want to consider bringing extra Saradomin brews and super restores instead of ranging or super combat potions, so they can kill the Great Olm without preparing supplies to save time. This is only recommended if the player has the [[sanguinesti staff]] for the mage hand, and/or the [[twisted bow]] or [[dragon hunter crossbow]] for the Olm head.
